==English==

===Etymology===
From ''[[welter]]'' and ''[[weight]]''.

====Adjective====
'''welter-weight'''

# {{boxing}} [[between]] [[light-weight]] and [[middle-weight]]

====Noun====
{{en-noun}}

# {{boxing}} a [[boxer]] weighing more than a [[light-weight]] boxer and less than a [[middle-weight]] boxer; someone boxing in the [[welter-weight]] class